respostas.texto:
location part is appended to the alias.

To illustrate:

Let's say we have the config

location /static/ {
    root /var/www/app/static/;
    autoindex off;
}


In this case the final path that Nginx will …  formed as

/var/www/app/static


The case of trailing slash for alias directive

There is no definitive guideline about whether a trailing slash is mandatory per Nginx documentation, but a common …

